**Description:** **: This Python script is designed as a web search and scraping tool using Ollama. It initializes tools for web scraping, Google search, Bing search, and Perplexity AI search. The script processes user inputs, generates responses from an LLM model, executes the appropriate tool based on the input, and handles errors. It runs an interactive loop in the main function to accept user commands asynchronously.

